  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together olive oil, garlic, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the sliced chili peppers to the bowl and stir to combine.",
    "Add the shrimp to the bowl and toss to coat with the marinade.",
    "Grill the shrimp for 2-3 minutes per side, or until pink and cooked through.",
    "Cook the vermicelli rice noodles according to package instructions.",
    "In a large serving bowl, combine the cooked noodles, grilled shrimp, and marinade.",
